channel.title: Project Frozn Fury [PFF] ~ 653 Items ~ 634 Chars ~ 602 Anims ~ 1k + Downloads
channel.description:
Hello fellow RSPS people, I have recently been working on this project, mainly client sided but here it is.
[size=18pt][b]I DO NOT GIVE PERMISSION FOR THIS TO BE POSTED ON ANY OTHER SITE![/b][/size]
[size=18pt]*NOTE* This is Rune MTP so it doesn't have npc drops unless you find a fix for it, I have not seen a fix for it yet.[/size]
Don't say you've seen it been released somewhere because it hasn't, for it isn't a leeched server.
[u][b][size=12pt]Downloads:[/size][/b][/u] [s]50[/s] [s]100[/s] [s]250[/s] [s]500[/s] [s]1000[/s] 1500 3000 (Downloads include both UppIt & MediaFire & also both old downloads & updated ones.)
Please post if you have downloaded it. Rate/Hate
- Auto-Mass save every 10 seconds. - Almost all skills are working/added except for a few I didn't bother with like Agility and Dungeoneering isn't full added. - Prayer tab with Rapid Renewal, Rigour, and Augury. - Curse prayers. - Quick prayers for curses and normal prayer. - Lunar interface fixed with Group Vengeance. - Minigames like Duel Arena, Barrows, Fight pits, and others fully working. - Boss's like KBD, Godwars, Daggs, and Chaos Ele. - 653 items. - 634 Characters. - 602 Animations. - 602 Gfx. - 474, 508, and 562 gameframes. - x10 and normal hitting with new hitmarks. - Added tab hovering my way because couldn't add them the other way. - Custom quick chat interface when quick chat icon is clicked. - New Friends and Ignore tab/list. - Much more to find out! Just download it.
